6,0.14527518,0.03005755,0.02242679,-0.01224898,-0.00337772,-0.01582251,0.10966110,-0.00559468,-0.04055344,0.00296833,0.01232321,0.00895089,0.03979967,-0.10291378,-0.02511406,0.04884044,0.00071075,-0.01518209,-0.00394866,0.05962384,0.04625479,-0.02944079,0.03668104,-0.01207135,-0.04609401,-0.01369183,-0.02050547,-0.01277925,-0.01017940,-0.01608415,0.06344315,-0.03685617,0.00652806,0.05640757,-0.05687601,0.03760320,-0.03895362,0.01510147,0.01395951,-0.02865131,0.09297178,-0.02341477,0.01418280]',E'Fix a broken chat input {/*fix-a-broken-chat-input*/}\n\nreturn (\n    <>\n      <input\n        disabled={isSending}\n        value={text}\n        onChange={e => setText(e.target.value)}\n      />\n      <button\n        disabled={isSending}\n        onClick={handleSend}>\n        {isSending ? ''Sending...'' : ''Send''}\n      </button>\n      {isSending &&\n        <button onClick={handleUndo}>\n          Undo\n        </button>\n      }\n    </>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n</Sandpack>\n\n</Solution>','{"source": "react", "version": "19", "language": "typescript", "title": "Referencing Values With Refs", "section_title": "referencing-values-with-refs", "url": "https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/referencing-values-with-refs.md", "topics": "react,hooks,referencing,values,with,refs", "categories": "web,typescript,frontend,spa"}');
